title: Top 10 RB Rankings + Waller Watch, Target Goblins - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/11
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, rankings week continues with arguably the most important fantasy position: running backs! Andy, Mike, and Jason count down their Top 10 running backs for the 2021 season! Plus, injury news out of training camp and a new edition of Buy or Sell. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 11th, 2021.
  
 Dominate your fantasy football draft with the 2021 Ultimate Draft Kit -- get the Draft Analyzer with the UDK+

 (11:45) - NFL News
 (23:55) - Top 10 Running Back Rankings
